page.title: 20Andrew (Continued)
page.content: represent where we were on the map.When we got back to school we went to dinner. For dinner I had Texas hash,boiled rice, peas and carrots and for pudding I had icecream and chocolate crackle. From one o'clock to Two I did a piece of writing. Then we played rounders.I went home at ten past three and played in the garden until my mum called me in for tea.After tea, I went out to play with my friends. We played football. After that I came in to watch T.V. Then I washed, brushed my teeth and went to bed.
